title: 3  Re-enrollment
text:
This chart shows the percentage of eligible students from last semester who re-enrolled for the current term. Eligible students are those who have not graduated and have no active holds (bursar, academic, or otherwise). Each segment displays both the percentage and number of students.
Please  Click here  for a list of eligible but not enrolled students and their contact information.
